txt.en: 'This'll do! Hope the beetles didn't give you too much trouble. I've heard they can be nasty.'
'Those beetles in Ghax-hophra have nests full of tasty little grubs. Just head north of Kafagur, and you'll see what I mean!'
You've collected a good amount of beetle larvae.\n\nYou should bring them to Shulgolb at Kafagur.
Shulgolb has asked you to collect larvae from beetle nests on Ghax-hophra.\n\nGhax-hophra is located north of Kafagur.
